message.content:
Case Based, Rule Learning

Explanation: 
This paper belongs to the sub-category of Case Based AI because it focuses on conversational case-based reasoning systems and how to improve their performance through automated revision of case libraries. The paper also belongs to the sub-category of Rule Learning because it describes an automated inductive approach for revising case libraries to increase their conformance with design guidelines. This approach involves learning rules from existing case libraries and using them to revise the libraries.
